Sentencas: Reversible solid oxide cells (RSOCs) as clean and efficient electrochemical conversion and storage devices have received much attention.
Titulo: Sr-free orthorhombic perovskite Pr0.8Ca0.2Fe0.8Co0.2O3-8 as a high-performance air electrode for reversible solid oxide cell

Sentencas: PrFeO3-8 has been investigated to obtain excellent performance when it is used as air electrode for RSOCs.
Titulo: Sr-free orthorhombic perovskite Pr0.8Ca0.2Fe0.8Co0.2O3-8 as a high-performance air electrode for reversible solid oxide cell

Sentencas: In this work, we investigate a novel PrFeO3-8 based orthorhombic perovskite oxide Pr0.8Ca0.2Fe0.8Co0.2O3-8 and use it as the air electrode of RSOCs.
Titulo: Sr-free orthorhombic perovskite Pr0.8Ca0.2Fe0.8Co0.2O3-8 as a high-performance air electrode for reversible solid oxide cell

Sentencas: The electrochemical performance of this cell with Pr0.8Ca0.2Fe0.8Co0.2O3-8 electrode is presented in detail.
Titulo: Sr-free orthorhombic perovskite Pr0.8Ca0.2Fe0.8Co0.2O3-8 as a high-performance air electrode for reversible solid oxide cell

Sentencas: The highest power density at 850 C can reach 1.762 W cm(-2) in fuel cell mode using hydrogen as fuel.
Titulo: Sr-free orthorhombic perovskite Pr0.8Ca0.2Fe0.8Co0.2O3-8 as a high-performance air electrode for reversible solid oxide cell

Sentencas: And the electrolysis current density of 2.23 A cm(-2) at 850 C can be achieved under the condition of 50 vol % absolute humidity at 1.3 V in electrolysis cell mode.
Titulo: Sr-free orthorhombic perovskite Pr0.8Ca0.2Fe0.8Co0.2O3-8 as a high-performance air electrode for reversible solid oxide cell

Sentencas: Moreover, during a long-term operation of up to 200 h, this cell can remain stable and shows good reversibility in two modes.
Titulo: Sr-free orthorhombic perovskite Pr0.8Ca0.2Fe0.8Co0.2O3-8 as a high-performance air electrode for reversible solid oxide cell

Sentencas: These results demonstrate that the perovskite Pr0.8Ca0.2Fe0.8Co0.2O3-8 is promising air electrode for RSOCs.
Titulo: Sr-free orthorhombic perovskite Pr0.8Ca0.2Fe0.8Co0.2O3-8 as a high-performance air electrode for reversible solid oxide cell
